info.name: The Headstart post icons for tumblr
info.description: Part of a theme for The Headstart - Replaces tumblr post icons with pictures of the band

style.css:
@-moz-document url-prefix("http://www.tumblr.com"), url-prefix('https://www.tumblr.com')   { .new_post_label{ font-size:0px !important; } .new_post_label_icon{background-image:none !important} /* Code repaired by admin. See http://forum.userstyles.org/discussion/37591/attempting-to-mass-fix-broken-tumblr-dash-icon-styles */
#new_post{ background: url(http://25.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_mbq9x3Tk7y1rgoq1io1_r1_500.png) center no-repeat !important; background-color:#fff !important; } img[src*="http://25.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_mbq9x3Tk7y1rgoq1io1_r1_500.png"]{ width:0; height:70px; padding-right:250px; opacity: 0; } }
